cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a Gaussian Mixture Model (GMM) and statistical properties of local neighborhoods suggest a machine learning approach (cs.AI) and a focus on feature extraction (cs.LG). The use of a multi-layer array and the evaluation of the proposed method on a dataset suggest a multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) focus.
